Package com.intellij.openapi.roots

Class JavaProjectModelModifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.roots.JavaProjectModelModifier
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IdeaProjectModelModifier

    public abstract class JavaProjectModelModifier
extends java.lang.Object
    Register implementation of this extension to support custom dependency management system for JavaProjectModelModificationService. The default implementation which modify IDEA's project model directly is registered as the last extension so it'll be executed if all other extensions refuse to handle modification by returning null.
    See Also:
    JavaProjectModelModificationService

      • addModuleDependency

        public Promise<java.lang.Void> addModuleDependency(Module from,
                                                   Module to,
                                                   DependencyScope scope,
                                                   boolean exported)
        Implementation of this method should add dependency from module from to module to with scope scope accordingly to this dependencies management system. If it takes some time to propagate changes in the external project configuration to IDEA's project model the method may schedule this work for asynchronous execution and return Promise instance which will be fulfilled when the work is done.
        Returns:
        Promise instance if dependencies between these modules can be handled by this dependencies management system or null otherwise
